<sect2>
<title>Introduction to <application>whois</application></title>

<para>whois is a client-side application which queries the whois
directory service for information pertaining to a particular domain
name. <!--Note that you already have this program from your LFS
installation, it can handle COM, NET and EDU queries. You will need
this application for any other domains. --></para>

